data.description:
-2 car garage that includes (2) attached storage rooms and a private driveway 
-oversized master bedroom with a walk-in closet and en-suite that has his/ her vanities, jacuzzi tub, and a separate shower
-kitchen has lots of counter space, a breakfast area and an eat-in dinning room (currently used as an office)
-Large living room with vaulted ceilings, wall to wall bookshelf storage, lots of natural light and semi-open concept
-four seasons, heated and cooled sunroom with 180 degree views of the spacious backyard and includes a separate sink
-two guest rooms with large closest
-shared guest bathroom with his/ her vanity and a separate toilet/ shower room for privacy 
-large finished upstairs heated and cooled bonus room that would make a great game room/ kids room/ man or woman cave.
data.whatILove: I love the huge back yard and secluded privacy that this lot provides. Located on a dead end street next to a field, this private yard provides a peaceful escape within city limits.
